description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents M83 performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded October 2, 2023.

Songs:
Water Deep
Oceans Niagara
Run Into Flowers
Gone
Amnesia
Earth To Sea
Noise

Anthony Gonzalez - Vocals, Guitar
Kaela Bratcher - Vocals, Keys
Theophile Antolines - Guitar
Clement Libes - Bass Violin
Joe Berry - Keys, Sax, eFlute
Julien Aoufi - Drums

Host: Cheryl Waters
Audio Engineers: Jon Roberts & Kevin Suggs
Guest Audio Engineers: Robbie Barr, Aaron Dupree & Robin Kibble
Audio Mixer & Mastering:  Brian Batz 
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro, Scott Holpainen & Jonathan Jacobson
Editor: Jim Beckmann
